Assuming Ubuntu, if amazon linux, aws cli will be there by default. 

apt-get update 
apt install python-pip

 
pip install awscli 
pip install boto

 aws --version

 
 Now create user in aws IAM
 =============================
 
1.  Go to IAM, create user and pwd
 
2.  enable programatic access
 
3.  assign an existing policy of Admin Access
 
4. Note down the Credentials
 
